snippet.title: Forbidden Planet
snippet.description:
"Forbidden Planet" is a Space Strategy Game for Android phones. 

You control a small spaceship and your main goal is to protect your own home planet. Explore the universe for resources.  Colonize other planets. Defend from the asteroids. Stay alive.

Demo : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Faton.forbidden_planet&hl=en

Full Version : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Gaffas.UFOTU
